originalText.text: Love RA Travel! Will use them again and have already recommended them to several friends! They exceeded our expectations and created an awesome experience for us!  An attentive staff (Jane & Gaelle) checked on us and updated us regularly, even with the big time difference. Great hotels, flights, excursions, drivers, etc.

originalText.text: As the CEO and founder of a hospitality consulting firm, I look for very detailed and top of the line service when it comes to my clients and team travel needs. RA Travel is truly the essence of stellar service. Extremely friendly staff offering 24/7 accessibility, special rates and amenities to all global hotel brands, and transportation services! RA Travel does it all to perfection!

originalText.text:
What I truly appreciated about my experience with this agency was their ability to make me feel as though I was their only client. I have always wanted to organize a family trip to Europe and my agent Jane gave me a peace of mind, knowing that I would be receiving the best possible rates and fares. It also turned out that the agency has pretty sound relationships with so many different hotels & resorts around the world and they took such great care of my family & I.

I will also say, my agent in particular knew what she was selling as she has personally visited these hotels and traveled to a multitude of destinations, I was in shock. She also offered excursions, restaurants, and activities customized to the interests of my family. I put off this trip for so long because of the nerve racking process of organizing everything, so thank you RA travel for going above and beyond.
